data.description: Charming single-family attached home in Lemoore, CA, featuring 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms with 1233 sqft living space. Recently renovated with new flooring, baseboard, door casing, HVAC, breaker panel, and updated light fixtures throughout. Enjoy a comfortable and stylish living space in this well-maintained property. Schedule a private showing today and don't miss out on making this home yours!
